{"id": "1292887806179541135", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "之后是哈姆林，本来都是废案了但是千呼万唤始出来，也看到有人分析pv的弦乐对应弥萨格大学，管乐是提灯，打击乐是哈姆林自己（影子是国际象棋）。\n而且PV也没有啥字，乐谱看上去都是瞎写的，反正我是看不得这个.jpg\n只有最后大标题有点字：", "timestamp": "2024-10-07T16:34:33.687000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-10-07T16:41:15.663000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1292888129987940392", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "最上面是弥萨格大学。\n中间最大的英文是版本名。\n下面是校徽，校徽上面是哈姆林的英文签名。\n之后下面又是几句老话。", "timestamp": "2024-10-07T16:35:50.889000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1292888129623031818", "filename": "Image_1728318866492.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1214398, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1292888129623031818/Image_1728318866492.png?ex=69cca0a6&is=69cb4f26&hm=e185c0a7b2d7395d79402e36c58b5bed8d290ee4f87f8c7916571aeefa2b1651&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
